    Player      AS player,

    SELECT
        DISTINCT
        club,
        club_url
    FROM "dev"."main"."stg_club"
)

SELECT
    ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY club) AS club_id,
    club,
    club_url
FROM base

    m.match_id,
    m.match_date,
  
    dclub_home.club_id AS home_club_id,
    dclub_home.club AS home_club_name,
    dclub_away.club_id AS away_club_id,
    dclub_away.club AS away_club_name,

    m.ft_home_goals,
    m.ft_away_goals,
    m.ft_result,
    m.ht_home_goals,
